data.name: CustomSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value:
select "vw_AGREEMENT"."dtAgreement", "vw_AGREEMENT"."arProt", "vw_AGREEMENT"."kitchen", "vw_AGREEMENT"."closet", "vw_AGREEMENT"."doors", "vw_AGREEMENT"."PayInAdvance", "vw_AGREEMENT"."VatPrice", "vw_AGREEMENT"."Price", "vw_AGREEMENT"."EmpName", "vw_AGREEMENT"."CctName", "vw_AGREEMENT"."ID", "vw_CCT"."FatherName", "vw_CCT"."AREAS_Name", "vw_CCT"."DOY_Name", "vw_CCT"."afm"
from "dbo"."vw_AGREEMENT" "vw_AGREEMENT" inner join "dbo"."vw_CCT" "vw_CCT" on ("vw_CCT"."ID" = "vw_AGREEMENT"."cusID" ) where ("vw_AGREEMENT"."ID" = @OfferID)
